Klawisz dostêpu przechwytywania wideo
Allows defining global hotkey for starting and stopping video capture.

Wskazówki:
- Enabling this option will cause additional %SERVERPRODUCTNAME% process to be automatically started. The server provides video capture services to 3D applications and it cannot be unloaded until this option is disabled.
- Some applications (e.g. F.E.A.R.) may purposely block hotkeys by breaking low-level keyboard hook chains.
- Some hotkey combinations (e.g. <1>...<5>, <Ctrl>+<1>...<Ctrl>+<5> and <Ctrl>+<D>) are reserved and cannot be used.
